{"tid":956711,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE又倒下！TWICE忙翻MINA掛病號","createTime":"2018-12-26T13:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T19:09:54.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a29d6557ecbe07e5feac1fbdc9a722c00bc4ff41","tid":956711,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181225/640_992c618d82f33d0b8c18a301480b3f2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181225%2F640_992c618d82f33d0b8c18a301480b3f2d.jpg&h=b8943da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE今天下午以黑白相兼的帥氣造型出席《SBS歌謠大戰》紅毯。韓聯社<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團「TWICE」出道3年，去年進軍日本後，日、韓兩地蠟燭兩頭燒，幾乎沒時間休息。繼台灣成員周子瑜上月底在宣傳期間掛病號後，今日本成員MINA在出席完《SBS歌謠大戰》紅毯後，經紀公司「JYP娛樂」發出官方聲明，表示「MINA因健康上的理由將不參加今天的活動」。<br />\n <br />\n「TWICE」出道以來工作滿檔，甚至被粉絲譽為是「模範勞工」，今年光是在韓國包含改版專輯就推出了4張，加上她們積極拓展日本市場，在日本通告也滿檔，經常日、韓兩地跑。先前曝光的影片中，定延就吐露心境表示很想成為成員支柱，卻無法，她邊說邊落淚：「我們在粉絲面前展現活潑的樣子，但經常無法掩飾疲憊，很對不起大家。」<br />\n <br />\nMINA雖已完成《SBS歌謠大戰》事前錄製部分，也出席了紅毯，但因健康問題無奈缺席現場直播。粉絲得知消息後滿是心疼，盼她能好好休息，不過TWICE接下來除了要參加各大電視台年底歌唱節目、頒獎典禮外，31日還要到日本出席《紅白歌唱大賽》，毫無休息時間，JYP在聲明中強調接下來的行程若有變動，會視狀況另行公布。<br />\n<br />\n心痛死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3049da8da63035f0d9b8ee34e82efc545e53441c","tid":956711,"uid":28920,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DT0zPMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT0zPMw.png&h=81fd5f29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnfDwZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnfDwZR.png&h=39f55b43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27c9532d77a3d436cf75975721eca8bbacd0c1cc","tid":956711,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3049da8da63035f0d9b8ee34e82efc545e53441c","tid":956711,"uid":28920,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DT0zPMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT0zPMw.png&h=81fd5f29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnfDwZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnfDwZR.png&h=39f55b43&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"???"},{"pid":"dae35052362bdb6feda5e7538c95ad19c4fd5688","tid":956711,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"咸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c334e1b6d6d1cbca7b523cc04bf6ba67271917","tid":956711,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"唔怪得E排唱歌好似呻吟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a860e245d0db76c957e7da1f87255defe5f76d26","tid":956711,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8af3f50ca7dec7f70f8894d894e0729ce12a0a0d","tid":956711,"uid":86727,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"好耐之前就已經有人講過TWICE回歸過密-__-"},{"pid":"83a60f1dab1d186f651893bb4ae324aa64e672a6","tid":956711,"uid":58374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T17:33:39.000Z","msg":"子瑜企得幾有 sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0413550103073e12e72bc238c97bab280c411d8f","tid":956711,"uid":136900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T19:09:54.000Z","msg":"個個都見到條腿縫<br />\n唯獨支瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces